# Cloudflare Pages response headers
# Applied to every path. Tighter rules can be scoped with path globs.
# Keep these in sync with the QA security baseline. CSP is intentionally
# omitted here because it must be tuned alongside Google AdSense, GA4, and
# GTM domains in a separate change.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=(), interest-cohort=()
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin-allow-popups
